          h4 Proposed design
          p Willie K. Hocker’s design submitted to the flag contest.
        li.flag-item
          span.flag: img(src='/assets/images/flag-arkansas-1913-1923.svg')
          h4 1913-1923
          p “Arkanas” is added to the Hocker design.
        li.flag-item
          span.flag: img(src='/assets/images/flag-arkansas-1923.svg')
          h4 1923-1924
          p A fourth star is added within the white diamond.
        li.flag-item
          span.flag: img(src='/assets/images/flag-arkansas.svg')
          h4 1924-Present
          p The fourth star is separated from the other three.

